---
<section class="relative bg-zinc-950 text-white py-24 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center relative z-20">
      <!-- Text Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <a href="https://wektor-kodu.vercel.app" target="_blank" title="Przejdź do usług programistycznych" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-400 hover:text-teal-400 hover:border-teal-400/30 transition-colors group">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-teal-400 animate-pulse"></span>
          Wektor Kodu - Tworzenie Stron WWW
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-3 h-3 group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>

        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
          Inżynierska Precyzja <br/>
          <span class="bg-clip-text text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-300">
            Druku 3D.
          </span> <br/>
          Od Pliku do Gotowej Części.
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-lg">
          Drukujemy gotowe projekty. Odtwarzamy uszkodzone części maszyn i aut. Projektujemy przymiary dla warsztatów. Jakość przemysłowa dzięki technologii AI i zamkniętej komorze.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="#kalkulator" class="bg-orange-700 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-orange-900/20 hover:shadow-orange-900/40 cursor-pointer text-center">
            WYCEŃ WYDRUK (Mam plik)
          </a>
          <a href="#kontakt" class="border border-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-900 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg transition-colors cursor-pointer text-center">
            DORABIANIE CZĘŚCI (Mam problem)
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Glow Effect -->
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[120%] h-[120%] bg-orange-500/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
        
        <!-- Image Container -->
        <div class="relative bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl aspect-square flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden shadow-2xl rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500">
          <video 
            src="/hero.mp4" 
            poster="/hero-poster.webp"
            preload="none"
            autoplay 
            loop 
            muted 
            playsinline 
            aria-hidden="true"
            tabindex="-1"
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
          ></video>
          
          <!-- Dark Overlay -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30 pointer-events-none"></div>
          
          <!-- Optional: Overlay gradient for depth -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-zinc-950/50 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
